<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,395,1970,1997]" pageId="5" pageNumber="356">Biological notes.</emphasis>
This species was found in a tropical dry forest, at 
<quantity box="[970,1042,1971,1997]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.09" pageId="5" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="109.0">109 m</quantity>
